<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Fire Emergency Services | Smart City Portal</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

body{
    background: linear-gradient(to right,#fff1f1,#ffffff);
}

/* Header */
.header{
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,#b11226,#e63946);
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:30px;
    animation: slideDown 1s ease;
}

.header h1{
    font-size:34px;
}

/* Emergency Note */
.emergency-note{
    width:85%;
    margin:30px auto;
    background:#ffe0e0;
    border-left:8px solid #b11226;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:10px;
    animation:pulse 2s infinite;
}

.emergency-note span{
    font-size:32px;
    font-weight:600;
    color:#b11226;
}

/* Container */
.container{
    width:90%;
    margin:auto;
}

/* Section title */
.section-title{
    text-align:center;
    font-size:28px;
    margin:40px 0 20px;
    color:#b11226;
}

/* Safety Tips */
.safety-tips{
    background:#fff4e0;
    border-left:8px solid #e67e22;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:10px;
    margin-bottom:30px;
    animation:fadeUp 1s ease;
}

.safety-tips h2{
    color:#e67e22;
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

.safety-tips ul{
    line-height:1.6;
    font-size:15px;
}

/* Address Form */
.form-box{
    background:white;
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:15px;
    box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    animation:fadeUp 1s ease;
}

.form-box label{
    font-weight:500;
    display:block;
    margin-bottom:8px;
}

.form-box textarea{
    width:100%;
    padding:14px;
    margin-bottom:25px;
    border-radius:10px;
    border:1px solid #ccc;
    font-size:15px;
}

.form-box button{
    width:100%;
    background:#b11226;
    color:white;
    padding:15px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:12px;
    font-size:17px;
    cursor:pointer;
    transition:0.3s;
}

.form-box button:hover{
    background:#8f0f1f;
}

/* Status Box */
.status-box{
    display:none;
    margin-top:30px;
    background:#e6ffe6;
    border-left:8px solid #2ecc71;
    padding:25px;
    border-radius:12px;
    animation:fadeUp 1s ease;
}

.status-box h3{
    color:#2ecc71;
}

/* Animations */
@keyframes slideDown{
    from{transform:translateY(-50px);opacity:0;}
    to{transform:translateY(0);opacity:1;}
}

@keyframes fadeUp{
    from{transform:translateY(40px);opacity:0;}
    to{transform:translateY(0);opacity:1;}
}

@keyframes pulse{
    0%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(177,18,38,0.5);}
    70%{box-shadow:0 0 0 15px rgba(177,18,38,0);}
    100%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(177,18,38,0);}
}

/* Footer */
footer{
    background:#222;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:15px;
    margin-top:40px;
    font-size:13px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="header">
    <h1>üî• Fire Emergency Services</h1>
    <p>Smart City Emergency Response ‚Äì India üáÆüá≥</p>
</div>

<div class="emergency-note">
    <h2>üö® Fire Emergency Call: <span>101</span></h2>
    <p>Use this portal to quickly notify the nearest fire station</p>
</div>

<div class="container">

    <!-- Safety Tips -->
    <div class="safety-tips">
        <h2>‚ö†Ô∏è Fire Safety Tips</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Keep a fire extinguisher accessible at home.</li>
            <li>Do not leave cooking unattended.</li>
            <li>Keep flammable materials away from heat sources.</li>
            <li>Install smoke detectors and check them regularly.</li>
            <li>Have an evacuation plan ready for your family.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title">üìç Enter Emergency Address</h2>

    <div class="form-box">
        <form action="/citizen/emergency/fire" method="POST">
        <label>Complete Address</label>
        <textarea id="address" name="address" rows="4" placeholder="House No, Street, Area, City, Pincode" required></textarea>
            
        <button type="submit">üöí Request Fire Service</button>
        </form>
        <!-- Status -->
        <div class="status-box" id="statusBox">
            <h3>‚úÖ Fire Services Dispatched!</h3>
            <p>Please follow the safety tips above while waiting for assistance.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    &copy; 2026 Smart City Portal | All Rights Reserved
</footer>


</body>
</html>
